<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="same-adv">same <strong><em>adv</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /seɪm/    美 /seɪm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>同样地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They will welcome you <strong>the same as</strong> they do me. 
他们会像欢迎我一样欢迎你。</p></div></div>